---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Contact Us - Book Your Free Strategy Call" description="Ready to transform your business with no-code solutions? Book a free strategy call with Yubea Labs and discover how we can help you launch in 2 weeks.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-purple-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Ready to Transform Your Business?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Book a free 30-minute strategy call and discover how we can help you launch your no-code solution in just 2 weeks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Options -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        
        <!-- Book a Call -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Book a Free Strategy Call</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Schedule a 30-minute call to discuss your project and get a custom quote.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Calendar Embed Placeholder -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-gray-400 mx-auto mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <p class="text-gray-500">Calendly Integration</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Calendar booking widget will be embedded here</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Choose a time that works for you. All calls are conducted via Zoom or Google Meet.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- What to Expect -->
          <div class="mt-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">What to expect in your call:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Discussion of your business needs and goals</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Recommendation of the best no-code solution</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Custom quote and timeline for your project</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700">Q&A about our process and next steps</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div>
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Send Us a Message</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Prefer to reach out directly? Fill out the form below and we'll get back to you within 24 hours.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Netlify Form -->
          <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" class="space-y-6">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label for="firstName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">First Name *</label>
                <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="lastName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Last Name *</label>
                <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Email Address *</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Company Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="company" name="company" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Phone Number</label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="service" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Service Interested In</label>
              <select id="service" name="service" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
                <option value="">Select a service</option>
                <option value="client-portal">Client Portal Starter Kit ($499)</option>
                <option value="mvp-launch">MVP Launch Pack ($799)</option>
                <option value="automation">Automation Setup ($299)</option>
                <option value="crm">CRM Buildout ($399)</option>
                <option value="custom">Custom Development</option>
                <option value="consultation">Just want to learn more</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="timeline" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">When do you need this completed?</label>
              <select id="timeline" name="timeline" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
                <option value="">Select timeline</option>
                <option value="asap">As soon as possible</option>
                <option value="1-month">Within 1 month</option>
                <option value="2-3-months">2-3 months</option>
                <option value="flexible">Flexible timeline</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Tell us about your project *</label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required placeholder="Describe your business needs, current challenges, and what you're hoping to achieve..." class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent"></textarea>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label for="budget" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Budget Range</label>
              <select id="budget" name="budget" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent">
                <option value="">Select budget range</option>
                <option value="under-500">Under $500</option>
                <option value="500-1000">$500 - $1,000</option>
                <option value="1000-2500">$1,000 - $2,500</option>
                <option value="2500-5000">$2,500 - $5,000</option>
                <option value="over-5000">Over $5,000</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
              <input type="checkbox" id="newsletter" name="newsletter" class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 focus:ring-blue-500 border-gray-300 rounded">
              <label for="newsletter" class="ml-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                I'd like to receive updates about no-code tips and Yubea Labs news
              </label>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-primary text-lg py-4">
              Send Message
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Information -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          We're here to help you succeed. Reach out through any of these channels.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Email -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Email Us</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">For general inquiries and support</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@yubealabs.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">hello@yubealabs.com</a>
        </div>

        <!-- WhatsApp -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893A11.821 11.821 0 0020.885 3.488"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">WhatsApp</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Quick questions and support</p>
          <a href="https://wa.me/971501234567" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-medium">+971 50 123 4567</a>
        </div>

        <!-- LinkedIn -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">LinkedIn</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">Connect with our team</p>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/yubealabs" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">@yubealabs</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Preview -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Common Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Quick answers to help you get started
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How quickly can you start?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We can typically start within 1-2 business days after our initial strategy call and project agreement.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you really deliver in 2 weeks?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes! Our Yubea Launch Loop™ process is specifically designed for 2-week delivery with a 95% on-time success rate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if I need changes later?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No-code solutions are easy to modify. We offer ongoing support plans or can train your team to make updates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is there a money-back guarantee?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We're confident in our work and will make revisions until you're satisfied. Our 98% client satisfaction rate speaks for itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/faqs" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">
          View all FAQs →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

